{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"c4e331a01b","title":"阳止胡宗南西进确保界石铺","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"dde1c4dc49","index":0,"year":1936,"month":9,"day":25,"articleId":"c4e331a01b"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji9-1","name":"毛泽东全集第9卷(1)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji9-1.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji9-1":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"3c31b72627","type":"paragraph","text":"阳止胡宗南西进确保界石铺","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"c4e331a01b"},{"id":"46417bb06a","type":"paragraph","text":"（1936年9月25日）彭，并告录：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"c4e331a01b"},{"id":"78aab7e987","type":"paragraph","text":"（一）四方面军决心向西从永靖渡河，谋占永登、凉州，其通渭部队二十四日撤去。据云渡河后以一部向中卫策应一方面军占宁夏。此事只好听他自己做去","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"c4e331a01b"},{"id":"c168850d60","type":"paragraph","text":"（二）但自前阻止胡敌西进仍属重要，十三团已否归还第一师，如未宜先派去加强之，界石铺仍应确保于我手中。此外是否可用一军团主力及八十一师占领固原、镇原线，威胁平凉、瓦亭请韵复。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"c4e331a01b"},{"id":"5d46e26907","type":"paragraph","text":"（三）二方面军如何动作，我们正考虑与电商中","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"c4e331a01b"},{"id":"6d8e97a009","type":"paragraph","text":"毛","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"c4e331a01b"},{"id":"c8bc8f7a18","type":"paragraph","text":"二十五日十四时","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"c4e331a01b"},{"id":"880c8ea1eb","type":"paragraph","text":"[1]这是毛泽东给红军第一方面军司令员、西方野战军司令员兼政治委员彭德怀并告第一方面军第一军团政治委员楚荣臻的电报。","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"c4e331a01b"},{"id":"c1e5de49d8","type":"paragraph","text":"[2]凉州，旧府名，即甘肃武威。","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"c4e331a01b"},{"id":"4897910411","type":"paragraph","text":"[3]胡，指胡宗南，当时任国民党军西北“”总司令部第一军军长兼第一师师长。","index":9,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"c4e331a01b"},{"id":"017c27bf31","type":"paragraph","text":"[4]瓦亭，镇名，位于宁夏固原县南部。","index":10,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"c4e331a01b"}],"page":{"id":"d564a90bbe","publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"c4e331a01b","start":169,"end":169}}}},"__N_SSG":true}